#: ../src/Tutorial/Dependent.md:507
msgid ""
"Implement function `fromList`, which converts a list of values to a `Vect` "
"of the same length. Use holes if you get stuck:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/Tutorial/Dependent.md:508
