msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/Tutorial/Dependent.md:864
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"   Note: This might be a challenging exercise, but make sure\n"
"   to give it a try. As usual, make use of holes if you get stuck!\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/Tutorial/Dependent.md:866
#, no-wrap
