"`Bifunctor`.  Likewise for `Bifoldable`/`Foldable` and "
"`Bitraversable`/`Traversable`."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '4. '
#: ../src/Tutorial/Traverse.md:1055
msgid ""
"We are now going to adjust `readCSV` in such a way that it decodes comment "
